Package: NUSS
Title: Mixed N-grams and Unigram Sequence Segmentation (NUSS)
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Oskar", "Kosch", , "contact@oskarkosch.com", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0003-2697-1393"))
Description: This package segments short texts - like hashtags -
    into the separated words sequence, and does so with the use of dictionary,
    which may be built on custom corpus of texts.
